近600人，录取人数约60人。要求学生提供GRE和GRE物理科目考试成绩，无最低GRE分数要求。该系所有学生均可以获得全额奖学金资助，包括TA/RA等。*(4)</p><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><p>斯坦福大学物理系有以下研究领域，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>原子、分子与光学物理（ATOMIC, MOLECULAR AND OPTICAL PHYSICS）</li>	<li>生物物理（BIOPHYSICS）</li>	<li>实验与观测天体物理学及宇宙学（EXPERIMENTAL &amp; OBSERVATIONAL ASTROPHYSICS AND COSMOLOGY）</li>	<li>实验凝聚态物理（EXPERIMENTAL CONDENSED MATTER PHYSICS）</li>	<li>实验粒子物理（EXPERIMENTAL PARTICLE PHYSICS）</li>	<li>其它研究（OTHER RESEARCH INTERESTS）</li>	<li>理论天体物理与宇宙学（THEORETICAL ASTROPHYSICS AND COSMOLOGY）</li>	<li>理论凝聚态物理（THEORETICAL CONDENSED MATTER PHYSICS）</li>	<li>理论粒子物理（THEORETICAL PARTICLE PHYSICS）*(5)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a href='https://physics.stanford.edu/academics/prospective-students/graduate-admissions' target='_blank'>Graduate Admissions</a> Stanford University</p><p>(2) <a href='https://gradadmissions.stanford.edu/applying/starting-your-application/required-exams' target='_blank'>Required Exams</a> Stanford University</p><p>(3) <a href='https://registrar.stanford.edu/students/tuition-and-fees/tuition-and-fees-2018-19' target='_blank'>Graduate Tuition, 2018-2019</a>&nbsp;Stanford University</p><p>(4) <a href='https://physics.stanford.edu/academics/prospective-students/graduate-admissions/financial-support' target='_blank'>Financial Support</a> Stanford University</p><p>(5) <a href='https://physics.stanford.edu/research' target='_blank'>RESEARCH AREAS AND HIGHLIGHTS</a> Stanford University</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>语言学</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.1%">			<p>USNEWS排名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:11.94%">			<p>-</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.1%">			<p>学费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:15.8%">			<p>$50,703</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.32%">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.74%">			<p>12月4日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.1%">			<p>TOEFL要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:11.94%">			<p>100</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.1%">	