求申请者递交GRE成绩，并未设定有最低GRE分数要求，但一般录取学生的GRE数学百分比排名多在94%以上，写作多在4.5分以上。*(4)</p><p>该系奖学金形式均为Merit-based，无需单独申请，自动随Offer发放，但并非所有的学生都可以获得全额奖学金。*(5)</p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a href='https://economics.stanford.edu/graduate/admissions' target='_blank'>Admissions</a> Stanford University</p><p>(2) <a href='https://gradadmissions.stanford.edu/applying/starting-your-application/required-exams' target='_blank'>Required Exams</a> Stanford University</p><p>(3) <a href='https://registrar.stanford.edu/students/tuition-and-fees/tuition-and-fees-2018-19' target='_blank'>Graduate Tuition, 2018-2019</a>&nbsp;Stanford University</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=grPZ_x3EwgqXD4AxTTTTTTE5DMklcm1hZuaCZ91CGHalU9qVBrYf0jUfx9HfDF1W3mtQ3VbQ_P6z34gh' target='_blank'>FAQ-Department of Economics</a> Stanford University</p><p>(5) <a href='https://economics.stanford.edu/graduate/financial-support' target='_blank'>Financial Support</a> Stanford University</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>政治学</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.14%">			<p>USNEWS排名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:12.62%">			<p>1</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.1%">			<p>学费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:15.44%">			<p>$50,703</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.32%">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.4%">			<p>12月4日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.14%">			<p>TOEFL要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:12.62%">			<p>100</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.1%">			<p>GPA要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:15.44%">			<p>3.8</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.32%">			<p>可申请学期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.4%">			<p>秋季</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.14%">			<p>IELTS要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:12.62%">			<p>不接受</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.1%">			<p>GRE要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:15.44%">			<p>Required</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.32%">			<p>GRE Subject</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.4