福MBA开设的选修课包括以下领域：</p><ul>	<li>会计（Accounting）</li>	<li>创业管理（Entrepreneurship）</li>	<li>金融（Finance）</li>	<li>国际管理（Global management）</li>	<li>人力资源（Human resources）</li>	<li>信息技术（Information technology）</li>	<li>领导力（Leadership）</li>	<li>管理经济学（Managerial economics）</li>	<li>市场营销（Marketing）</li>	<li>运营管理（Operations）</li>	<li>组织行为学（Organizational behavior）</li>	<li>政治经济学（Political economics）</li>	<li>公共管理（Public management）</li>	<li>战略管理（Strategic management）*(8)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Nr20uKHuwN_n-gvu44444ocQ6iruZ2dOBH8H8KvGZ7WpZHr4kV6OZVAp6CrQBH_Kk78K3CQjB7QT3w1g2Qguj1acjsO7Vqhe8sg-kqhnjsO79s6WUQh_Y_4OAe-bcrVOVD-O00Pkce-HiLVK' target='_blank'>TOEFL, IELTS &amp; PTE</a> Stanford University</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=9rpcSXLhwkcdGHTE44DtpC15aAkvvrRdUA0-kDfqfRNOxdwFOddLyik3-idLaBZkmbxhYW-EQQquF5WBy6PEVdQLJeGShid8FJTk30m1au4B_fr6OcNVtOkHpBL3yTaiF2OzfpOOEPzBQ3ernhVFOUc' target='_blank'>Professional Experience</a> Stanford University</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=trmo1nqDw-IwELTNTcZOnbBCeJhi5ApzacRaifxFFWd43uypefigAGctRRFm_dvHmJafT_grLtBk1WYdFYy35BLn3NoU9nOJGHSJdapFmcivJG-6dLXkYTmYz' target='_blank'>MBA Deadlines</a> Stanford University</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=PrgaXqFFwX5FZyRg3333329dfGYO4BieGwoxoxeyiasUkZsga0Ff7abq7oRnlngjPdhXw0e3EpbO9y35_ksCBgdfjJK1wUIgq689q6-F9krxnM7BgM9qyK7ZILx8z' target='_blank'>Cost Summary-MBA</a> Stanford University</p><p>(5) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=4rjT-BkcLYq_Z87-ZZZZZnXg6y_xMG-Nx0qyqyWsRxz5r9zq-V2AOwB8OWrjDx3poGSsMnJwvPGQFKwk8TX627VGwvXAEoXEv9b0nYnPvEcbzJhqHXFdfG05-zdJbc8vAa_iq2637p5VdUTaTxVgr' target='_blank'>Entering Class Profile​</a> Stanford University</p><p>(6) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=wrYmhljekvECxLsdNNNNN7uU8AKtb1_ITLTLpnktgv2tTArl9e_t95xSvo0yBHL1kGw1royVBGyUru5lv2yCPHFxCkGOZr-Ldk