; Policy）</li>	<li>金融（Finance）</li>	<li>市场营销（Marketing）</li>	<li>信息技术与运营（Operations, Information &amp; Technology）</li>	<li>组织行为学（Organizational Behavior）</li>	<li>政治经济学（Political Economics）*(7)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ZrygfZiCLXmqlAsxMZkYk5hFCvzcTdr-dpPfvoE1tWsjkyvbdtvKP6z6P6qBXiGggcSt-8LB06htwoKct74ZFw9sehCv6DhLnembqUet1Ka1BfT6Si1OeBomAhLnIQyOUealssF' target='_blank'>GSB PhD Deadline &amp; Decisions</a> Stanford University</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=_r75g1qDLZv0OP6tjjjjjzhg6y_xMG-NJbIvIvGXAzxZ-FxtSv0pBqEXB6tP80ZtCDlLC3AXOWp27x0qiYBw6VSWdysRK6sfrgxJZlpm-mkX6F1xB_ThycTaL-h1MmOoysc' target='_blank'>GSB PhD Application Materials</a> Stanford University</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=wrYmhlZBwCpmLkIBwwwwwIA-weEp678NpUPOPOucyM9vcU9qADj3crIRcGfM1ZA0HqJLzHq7Qe8GTOWcCue0SGw7COc2lhcUJaHCXilkbTOmMBlDxQo6CloxEYi6Uel3CmjGwtYbxT_e-YtapwoQlXU2YEUTfYnWL3qonKbEUx' target='_blank'>International Applicants-PhD GSB</a> Stanford University</p><p>(4) <a href='https://registrar.stanford.edu/students/tuition-and-fees/tuition-and-fees-2018-19' target='_blank'>Graduate Tuition, 202</a><a href='https://gradadmissions.stanford.edu/admitted-students/financing-graduate-study/estimated-expense-budget' target='_blank'>0-21</a>&nbsp;Stanford University</p><p>(5) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=MrO2caRVLQjzhVzPw4F_mAhktgH5aoFh95cDxudMrKv6NG7B1wI4uoVtZbr7t7inyqVS906O5NW7ShqM5-ad_aptldpkPH--OnyTHtjwBrBebNQa' target='_blank'>GSB PhD Financial Aid</a> Stanford University</p><p>(6) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=DroIGDyakAlE5Ynn77777lBA5Ls6kVrtTCs1s1M-QM6Z076nGdeubs61bkilhNCXDUn-KRQgSNrujHwxdMIyQbSD3AFO2pFXON7iRfGSnHz8aq_BDjrURyrCQNC4G0x1jNbFg-2bA38b9GoUE' target='_blank'>GMAT &amp; GRE-PhD GSB</a> Stanford University</p><p>(7) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=-rGz4OstwQ4TaJionnnnn_2SJruZ2dOBH8H8KvGZ7WpZHr4kV6OZVAp6CrQBH_Kk78K38z2trAE-4jDyQBu14z2NQd2IxnEIhSII9SXpLUWGWo3ThGY9' target='_blank'>GSB PhD Fields of Study</a> Stanford University</p><p>(8) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=pr9ExTIBwCpmL8Dn1BY592fSb_27ikFdFBjHwTxAdiLf7joK_hwLAHVLjoFtlPHpp9AhPUgTiLd-OWRCtZV8VdiLdcPzzCzhLT0W6xvdhbVnjLNChjzj2teh5f-yTbRnMEdVMPXysgeFXlOvljKfBdA3OMCDv1Mq8_ONvs' target='_blank'>Entering Class Profile</a> Stanford University</p><h3>商学硕士</h3><p>斯坦福大学商学硕士项目（MSx Program）为期1年，属全日制授课项目，主要是为有多年管理领导经验者提供的。与MBA项目不同的是，该项目录取的职业中期者有约90人，国际学生占66%，平均工作经验12年，最低也要8年。申请者可同时申请MBA和硕士项目，仅需缴纳一次申请费，约计275美金。基于此，本科应届毕业生基本上是无法申请该项目的。*(1)(2)</p><p><strong>课程设置</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:14.52%">			<p>会计</p>			</td>			<td style="width:29.98%">			<p>Accounting</p>			</td>			<td style="width:21.1%">			<p>市场营销管理</p>			</td>			<td style="width:34.4%">			<p>Marketing Management</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:14.52%">			<p>经济学</p>			</td>			<td style="width:29.98%">			<p>Economics</p>			</td>			<td style="width:21.1%">			<p>运营</p>			</td>			<td style="width:34.4%">			<p>Operations</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:14.52%">			<p>职业道德</p>			</td>			<td style="width:29.98%">			<p>Ethics</p>			</td>			<td style="width:21.1%">			<p>战略与市场营销</p>			</td>			<td style="width:34.4%">			<p>Strategy Beyond Markets</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:14.52%">			<p>金融</p>			</td>			<td style="width:29.98%">			<p>Finance</p>			</td>			<td style="width:21.1%">			<p>数据与决策</p>			</td>			<td style="width:34.4%">			<p>Data and Decisions</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:14.52%">			<p>竞争战略</p>			</td>			<td style="width:29.98%">			<p>Competitive Strategy</p>			</td>			<td style="width:21.1%">			<p>商业谈判</p>			</td>			<td style="width:34.4%">			<p>Negotiations</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:14.52%">			<p>组织设计</p>			</td>			<td colspan="3" style="width:85.48%">			<p>Organization Design</p>			</td>		</tr>	</tbody></table><p>*(3)</p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=BraKR4YqweEscMLWQQQQQQCU4zOgEq7CTL3d3dy5nzrqdgrXvYOmYeiJYP8dbjY7En58Bh8CgbNKXMHv04wp' target='_blank'>Academic Experience</a> Stanford University</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=8rL6TCP0Lr9DfQRgzIF4-TS3m5WS9OEw0d7_hC-PS_FoJ65WmahWlF4g7QSJZ98JtKR-3NCEker9tKyN9eNAM-sZAMq7-ah7XofSFc6rhYP' target='_blank'>Admission</a> Stanford University</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=PrgaXq8WLs_unRQq2PlyVhtX8lUGblZtssnqZMJ6tNEaCtfkMS9PUV_ZFHrA6KpASHMSXl0tDZ1drAq7HkyMBtNVG641_Bht-0qXlCUao_LziZJttPD8PiOXHq-_ZL81jttwEhFtQw' target='_blank'>Curriculum</a> Stanford University</p><h2>工程学院</h2><p>斯坦福大学工程学院（School of Engineering）共有9个系外加1个研究中心招收研究生，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>航空航天工程系（Department of Aeronautics &amp; Astronautics）</li>	<li>生物工程系（Department of Bioengineering）</li>	<li>化学工程系（Department of Chemical Engineering）</li>	<li>土木与环境工程系（Department of Civil &amp; Environmental Engineering）</li>	<li>计算机科学系（Department of Computer Science）</li>	<li>电气工程系（Department of Electrical Engineering）</li>	<li>管理科学与工程系（Department of Management Science &amp; Engineering）</li>	<li>材料科学与工程系（Department of Materials Science &amp; Engineering）</li>	<li>机械工程系（Department of Mechanical Engineering）</li>	<li>计算与数学工程所（Institute for Computational &amp; Mathematical Engineering）*(1)(2)</li></ul><p><strong>申请说明</strong></p><p>斯坦福大学工程学院研究生国际学生占比约40%，所有斯坦福工程学院的本科生都可申请本硕连读直接入读硕士项目。对国内学生而言，该学院研究生的基本申请要求如下：</p><ul>	<li>学位背景要求：四年制正规大学本科毕业并获得学士学位*(3)</li>	<li>语言要求：除工程学院开设的部分硕士学位项目外，其余项目均要求TOEFL不低于100分，无单项要求，不接受IELTS成绩；工程学硕士要求TOEFL不低于89分，同样无单项要求，同样不接受IELTS成绩*(4)</li>	<li>GPA要求：未设定有最低GPA分数要求</li>	<li>GRE要求：所有专业均需要有GRE成绩，法学院、医学院、商学院除外，它们要求的分别是LSAT、MCAT以及GMAT*(5)</li>	<li>申请时间：多在12月初或1月初截止申请</li></ul><p><strong>费用与奖学金</strong></p><p>斯坦福大学工程学院的奖学金均为Merit-based形式，无需单独申请，自动随offer发放。现有超过180名学生获得了奖学金资助，其中有65-70名学生获得的是斯坦福研究生院提供的Feollowship。*(2)</p><p><strong>费用列表（2018-19</strong><strong>学年）：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:35.22%">			<p>支出项目</p>			</td>			<td style="width:22.74%">			<p>每学期（Quarter）</p>			</td>			<td style="width:29.64%">			<p>三个学期（秋、冬、春）</p>			</td>			<td style="width:12.4%">			<p>四个学期</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:35.22%">			<p>学费（11-18个学分）</p>			</td>			<td style="width:22.74%">			<p>-</p>			</td>			<td style="width:29.64%">			<p>$54,015</p>			</td>			<td style="width:12.4%">-</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:35.22%">			<p>住宿费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:22.74%">			<p>$4,910</p>			</td>			<td style="width:29.64%">			<p>$14,730</p>			</td>			<td style="width:12.4%">			<p>$18,606</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:35.22%">			<p>膳费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:22.74%">			<p>$1,985</p>			</td>			<td style="width:29.64%">			<p>$5,955</p>			</td>			<td style="width:12.4%">			<p>$7,940</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:35.22%">			<p>个人花费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:22.74%">			<p>$1,380</p>			</td>			<td style="width:29.64%">			<p>$4,140</p>			</td>			<td style="width:12.4%">			<p>$5,520</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:35.22%">			<p>交通费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:22.74%">			<p>$440</p>			</td>			<td style="width:29.64%">			<p>$1,320</p>			</td>			<td style="width:12.4%">			<p>$1,760</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:35.22%">			<p>书本与设备费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:22.74%">			<p>$510</p>			</td>			<td style="width:29.64%">			<p>$1,530</p>			</td>			<td style="width:12.4%">			<p>$2,040</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:35.22%">			<p>校园医疗服务费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:22.74%">			<p>$217</p>			</td>			<td style="width:29.64%">			<p>$651</p>			</td>			<td style="width:12.4%">			<p>$868</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:35.22%">			<p>医疗保险费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:22.74%">			<p>$1,736</p>			</td>			<td style="width