boratory</li>	<li>Security Lab</li>	<li>Simbios</li>	<li>Smart Products Design Lab</li>	<li>Space and Systems Development Laboratory</li>	<li>Space, Telecommunications and Radioscience Laboratory</li>	<li>Stanford Artificial Intelligence Laboratory</li>	<li>Stanford Center for Professional Development</li>	<li>Stanford Center for Societal Networks</li>	<li>Stanford Compression Forum</li>	<li>Stanford Nano Center</li>	<li>Stanford Nanocharacterization Laboratory</li>	<li>Stanford Nanofabrication Facility</li>	<li>Stanford Synchrotron Radiation Lightsource</li>	<li>Stanford Technology Ventures Program</li>	<li>Structures and Composites Laboratory</li>	<li>Systems Optimization Laboratory</li>	<li>The Bob and Norma Street Environmental Fluid Mechanics Laboratory</li>	<li>TomKat Center for Sustainable Energy</li>	<li>Unsteady Flow Physics and Aeroacoustics Laboratory</li>	<li>US-Asia Technology Management Center*(7)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>工程学院研究生导师列表：<a href='https://engineering.stanford.edu/people/faculty/grid' target='_blank'>Faculty</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a href='https://engineering.stanford.edu/research-and-faculty/departments' target='_blank'>DEPARTMENTS-School of Engineering</a> Stanford University</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=pr9ExTdmLGCeMdm4ggggggKvSc8nsUQtXJoyX0oyZJ1vZOTtT98uZOH-rhPJbxmKDZhEMjyWx-PIxLpDe' target='_blank'>APPLYING TO STANFORD ENGINEERING</a> Stanford University</p><p>(3) <a href='https://gradadmissions.stanford.edu/applying/international-applicants' target='_blank'>International Academic Credentials</a> Stanford University</p><p>(4) <a href='https://gradadmissions.stanford.edu/about/frequently-asked-questions/international-students' target='_blank'>FAQs International Students</a> Stanford University</p><p>(5)&nbsp;<a href='https://gradadmissions.stanford.edu/about/frequently-asked-questions/gre-and-toefl' target='_blank'>FAQs-GRE &amp; TOEFL</a> Stanford University</p><p>(6) <a href='https://gradadmissions.stanford.edu/admitted-students/financing-graduate-study/estimated-expense-budget' target='_blank'>Graduate Tuition, 2018-2019</a>&nbsp;Stanford University</p><p>(7) <a href='https://engineering.stanford.edu/research-and-faculty/institutes-labs-and-centers' target='_blank'>Institutes, Labs and Centers</a> Stanford University</p><h3>数学与计算金融</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:82px">			<p>USNEWS排名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:58.8px">			<p>2</p>			</td>			<td style="width:81.2px">			<p>学费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:72.4px">			<p>$50,703</p>			</td>			<td style="width:81.2px">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:96.4px">			<p>12月3日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:82px">			<p>TOEFL要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:58.8px">			<p>113</p>			</td>			<td style="width:81.2px">			<p>GPA要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:72.4px">			<p>3.0</p>			</td>			<td style="width:81.2px">			<p>可申请学期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:96.4px">			<p>秋季</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:82px">			<p>IELTS要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:58.8px">			<p>不接受</p>			</td>			<td style="width:81.2px">			<p>GRE要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:72.4px">			<p>Required</p>			</td>			<td style="width:81.2px">			<p>GRE Subject</p>			</td>			<td style="width:96.4px">			<p>Not Required</p>			</td>		</tr>	</tbody></table><p>*(1)(2)(3)</p><p>注：</p><p>（1）此处排名为<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/2019USNEWS美国数学排名' target='_blank'>2019USNEWS美国数学排名</a></p><p>（2）此截止日期为博士申请截止日期，硕士申请日期为：1月7号。</p><p>（3）工程学院硕士的要求只有89分，但计算与数学工程所要求申请者的TOEFL最好不低于113分*(2)</p><p>（4）此处为2018-19学年平均每学期的费用参考，这里一般研究生和工程学项目的费用是按一学期修读11-18个学分来计算的，该区间内的学费费用是相同的。需要注意的是，该费用每年会有较小（不超过5%）的涨幅。斯坦福大学实行Quarter学期制，每学年分四个学期，分3次缴费，分别是秋季、冬季和春季*(3)</p><p><strong>申请说明</strong></p><p>斯坦福大学数学与计算金融（Mathematical &amp; Computational Finance）专业原名&ldquo;金融数学（Financial Mathematics）&rdquo;，隶属于文理学院，2014年秋季起改设于工程学院下属的计算与数学工程所（Institute for Computational &amp; Mathematical Engineering，缩写ICME），教员仍是原来班子。此处将其至于商学院之下介绍，是为照顾中国学生的习惯，该专业也即人们眼中常说的&ldquo;金融工程&rdquo;专业。</p><p>该专业研究生只提供MS项目，为期2年，以计算数学与计算机基础为主，要求申请者本科毕业，拥有数学或计算机专业背景，学习过线性代数、数值理论、概率、随机指数、实时分析和计算机编程，包括C++等课程。如有金融或企业相关工作或实习经验则更受欢迎。毕业生可选择就业或继续攻读博士学位。该专业奖学金较为有限，由研究生院和工程学院提供的两个Fellowship只向PhD学生提供，TA和RA一般只向老生开放，而唯一的非TA、RA、Fellowship奖学金也只是只向美国公民或永久居民开放的助学贷款（Loan），因此对该专业的新生来讲，基本上是没有任何奖学金来源的。 *(4)(5)</p><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>数学与计算金融专业研究生导师列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=wrYmhlEHLdft_268D4RYxMwmpCTLjVPtThAZ2HZkwkWi4nReNSfcbLJoB4agPENp6aZh_2ieac4RrjbcoNGSKanqODk6f9aatKxKxhgtvRS-3yj9qzj' target='_blank'>Faculty and Instructors</a></li>	<li>数学与计算金融专业在校硕士生列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=pr9ExTdnL9PXWjadvcljog-Oksh6wmjhELdxulaU-E85kPtzatr5_R9R66rYaNjeKYmto5qK94IGtDotIUM92wYZgx3_LKqGY' target='_blank'>MS Students</a></li>	<li>数学与计算金融专业在校博士生列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=pr9ExTHXku1DPNgq6yFGvVCuW98t4FNRimjtpA4wUMs5sWhTcCDumX7A_VUYpKGzhM7YqdXaNr1xmx9woiL8OP8jKxcf-5C2Sd' target='_blank'>PhD Students</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=trmo1nq8wiWP5A_N999999xZVOBqiQKpGwtYFIA7biZHr4kV6OtL-ewBK0JxSVZINQk7-6sgNYxKNi6xt46xmlBhGxX' target='_blank'>Deadlines</a>&nbsp;Stanford University</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=srULj0-Uws9rfa2M_nQ8-mBNiLsGz2mh6QALpZ-NOHd3S9oD5FhJpg7nlQffSnhPZcj1_m_sPnJt16mOmPTUJ1H8RdPLJcOFHgH9sv' target='_blank'>Application</a>&nbsp;Stanford University</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a href='https://registrar.stanford.edu/students/tuition-and-fees/tuition-and-fees-2018-19' target='_blank'>Tuition and Fees, 2018-19</a>&nbsp;Stanford University</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a href='https://icme.stanford.edu/academics/degrees' target='_blank'>Degree Programs</a>&nbsp;Stanford University</p><p>(5)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=MrO2caRSL1wLXKvskkkkkk7P-NZwyuJzXcm-GFv73