流体力学与水文硕士（Master of Environmental Fluid Mechanics and Hydrology）</li>	<li>可持续设计与施工硕士（Master of Sustainable Design and Construction）</li>	<li>环境与工程科学硕士（Master of Environmental and Engineering Sciences）</li>	<li>大气与能源硕士（Master of Atmosphere and Energy）*(4)</li>	<li>土木与环境工程博士（PhD in Civil and Environmental Engineering）：该项目共计135个学分。该项目以研究内容为主，需要撰写毕业论文，国际学生可申请TTA/RA或Fellowship奖学金，金额范围$1,000-$57,000*(5)(6)</li></ul><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><p>该系设有以下五个专业方向，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>大气与能源（Atmosphere and Energy）</li>	<li>建筑环境（The Built Environment）</li>	<li>水文环境（The Water Environment）*(7)</li></ul><p>此外，该系开设的研究实验室有：</p><ul>	<li>John A. Blume Earthquake Engineering Center</li>	<li>Center for Integrated Facility Engineering (CIFE)</li>	<li>Codiga Resource Recovery Center (CR2C)</li>	<li>Environmental Engineering and Science Lab (EESL)</li>	<li>The Bob and Norma Street Environmental Fluid Mechanics Laboratory (EFML)</li>	<li>Environmental Informatics Group</li>	<li>Global Projects Center (GPC)</li>	<li>National Performance of Dams Program (NPDP)</li>	<li>Project-Based Learning (PBL) Laboratory</li>	<li>Re-inventing the Nation&rsquo;s Urban Water Infrastructure (ReNUWIt)</li>	<li>Stanford Environmental &amp; Water Studies Summer Program</li>	<li>Sustainable Development &amp; Global Competitiveness (SDGC) Center*(8)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>土木与环境工程系研究生导师列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=wrYmhlZ5wfFe8hGn-----xjLRolh0mnySV9kurM5OfY12UHPSUpTsURvLXYJLXY3soyUmZ6J9fRc' target='_blank'>Faculty</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a href='https://gradadmissions.stanford.edu/applying' target='_blank'>Required Exams</a> Stanford University</p><p>(2) <a href='https://gradadmissions.stanford.edu/admitted-students/financing-graduate-study/estimated-expense-budget' target='_blank'>Graduate Tuition, 2018-2019</a>&nbsp;Stanford University</p><p>(3) <a href='https://cee.stanford.edu/admissions/application-timeline-deadlines' target='_blank'>&nbsp;Timeline &amp; Deadlines</