ng></p><p>材料科学与工程系开设的研究领域有：</p><ul>	<li>Computational Materials Science</li>	<li>Electronic, Photonic and Magnetic Materials</li>	<li>Energy Materials</li>	<li>Nano and Biomaterials</li>	<li>Nano-Characterization</li>	<li>Nano-Mechanics</li>	<li>Ultrafast Science*(7)</li></ul><p>此外，该系开设的研究实验室有：</p><ul>	<li>Bay Area Photovoltaic Consortium (BAPVC)</li>	<li>Bio-X</li>	<li>Center for Magnetic Nanotechnology (CMN)</li>	<li>Geballe Laboratory for Advanced Materials</li>	<li>Nanoscale Prototyping Laboratory</li>	<li>PULSE Institute for Ultrafast Energy Science</li>	<li>Stanford Center for Cancer Nanotechnology Excellence</li>	<li>Stanford Nanocharacterization Laboratory</li>	<li>Stanford Nanofabrication Facility</li>	<li>Stanford Photonics Research Center</li>	<li>Stanford Synchrotron Radiation Laboratory*(8)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>材料科学与工程系研究生导师列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=rrcuJRYuLRgWEzzr555555QkwSXx4APMZuH9fBHoUpF9QnY9rB29wgPxi2l_72bYUTs8jalzOty' target='_blank'>Faculty</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a href='https://gradadmissions.stanford.edu/applying' target='_blank'>Required Exams</a> Stanford University</p><p>(3) <a href='https://gradadmissions.stanford.edu/admitted-students/financing-graduate-study/estimated-expense-budget' target='_blank'>Graduate Tuition, 2017-2018</a> Stanford University</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=9rpcSXLAwVJpb8WLSSSSSShWyVJWYuBzTL21zZS5zf5MCjAKu_-RdOgRejNjJd56PjCiVZ9JPB3JR3HE6NiqoNw-yh9-bvtsau' target='_blank'>PhD Admissions</a> Stanford University</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=SrWl9LxQwtelk6MGa1zeevdVmcc4p-vzCda3rSFTFfwP4pLQTzrT-HErmaBFVI1O6hKhcZf7O-D_Fk7wUuviRzF2b3ELivBmqpGXMrehcZ4' target='_blank'>Master&rsquo;s Program</a> Stanford University</p><p>(5) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=jr4AscJnL9PXWNG5qqqqqqELlKfyC750d9Fwn36wAmaAoyHY1y4O0ySkQuZcev_9RvZYon1YHvZOm-H95uZfeurFdM' target='_blank'