e Tuition, 2018-2019</a>&nbsp;Stanford University</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=5rk_5oEXku1DPCCfYYYYYYH8us4OgQPBjZUwSZlmNsuyn9lTshr5IoJQ3vsC4wsxZXuxULjpgAlKEOpcUQpkUP7dRkegWSQ' target='_blank'>PhD Admissions</a> Mechanical Engineering Stanford University</p><p>(5) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=2rNMmQ1VwAbLSIj8xxxxxxIKIF1JyrZG_-dy0-15LSlkw8ufMpscsFMU0ClR-JkqjEpqZrAuo7ATShBCXm0HtTnWGjNEn-' target='_blank'>Financial Aid</a> Stanford University</p><p>(6) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ir67yhZ3L8zwPUQuKN3895aGUfdi1UkaWRGvwNtAqZxM4wf5mh2k7XIOr5-BIuV3Pr-SXc87BcmmtsEH6Bk4VqdfPdW6GIqdetWlf3h-aPuGswLFwdEKot0WawRRKqj2Nj-RtBeswp' target='_blank'>Admissions Frequently Asked Questions</a> Stanford University</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2>地球科学学院</h2><p>斯坦福大学地球科学学院（School of Earth Sciences）开设有以下四个系，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>能源工程系（Department of Energy Resources Engineering）</li>	<li>环境地球系统科学系（Department of Environmental Earth System Science）</li>	<li>地质与环境科学系（Department of Geological &amp; Environmental Sciences）</li>	<li>地球物理系（Department of Geophysics）*(1)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a href='https://earth.stanford.edu/academics/departments' target='_blank'>Departments-School of Earth Sciences</a> Stanford University</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>能源工程</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.34%">			<p>USNEWS排名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:12.56%">			<p>3</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.04%">			<p>学费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:15.4%">			<p>$54,015</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.32%">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.34%">			<p>12月10日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.34%">			<p>TOEFL要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:12.56%">			<p>100</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.04%">			<p>GPA要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:15.4%">			<p>3.0</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.32%">			<p>可申请学期</p>			</td>			<td 